Class ResupplyReqController

java.lang.Object
controllers.AbstractController
controllers.ResupplyReqController
public class ResupplyReqController extends AbstractController
ResupplyReqController is a controller for operation employee. It uses for handling and managing inventory stock. It extends AbstractController and overrides methods of it.
